.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, r&b
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, october, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the fan of indie##1
10. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | 7up     | fanta    | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b     | indie    | disco         |
| Birthday           | november         | april | october     | march        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

