.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, mango, potato, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, gardening, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, journalist, musician, teacher
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, mah-jongg, whist
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, lizard, snake
 1. the dancer is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the person eating potato##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the musician is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the dancer##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person playing snooker is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | kale       | mango     | potato     | pumpkin  |
| Hobby         | gardening  | skydiving | collecting | drawing  |
| Job           | journalist | dancer    | teacher    | musician |
| Game   | whist    | mah-jongg   | snooker | chess |
| Pet           | bird       | snake     | ferret     | lizard   |

