10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Sport    | rowing     | snowboarding  | weightlifting       | soccer      |
| Hobby       | singing    | writing        | collecting  | drawing      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, soul, dubstep, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of d&b##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of dubstep##1
10. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | video-games | magic-tricks | dancing  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | soul     | d&b      | rock |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | mexican     | brazilian    | british  |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | snake       | cat          | rat      |

