.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite, dahlia, bellflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, mystery, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, rowing, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, motorbike, ship
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who growsdahlia##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

