.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indian, indonesian, argentine
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard, social-worker
4 different pets are kept: cat, goat, goldfish, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship, snowmobile
 1. the social-worker is the british##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the social-worker is on the right of the indonesian##1
 4. the indian is on the left of the doctor##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is the argentine##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the indian##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 8. the doctor is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
10. the person eating grapes is the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Nationality       | indonesian       | british       | indian      | argentine |
| Job         | entrepreneur | social-worker | security-guard | doctor      |
| Pet         | cat          | snake         | goat           | goldfish    |
| Transport   | ship         | scooter       | snowmobile     | motorbike   |

 